data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and spacious home in Saddle Rock Ridge. The large and welcoming entry way opens onto a combined sitting area and dining area with wooden floors.  The doorway off the dining area leads to the large kitchen with lots of storage, cabinets space and a breakfast nook. The kitchen overlooks the living room area that features vaulted ceilings and an impressive chandelier. Just off the living room is a main floor office which is next to the main floor laundry room with access to the garage. The Three-car garage includes a solid, centrally-located work bench with 5/8" plywood surfaces. The upstairs of this home includes the master suite with walk-in closet. Also featured on the second floor are three additional bedrooms, one bathroom, and a roomy loft area that overlooks the main floor living room. The basement has been partially finished (with permits) and has been framed out, wired and drywalled in about 60-70% of the area. It is laid out so that a half bath can be added before completion of the remaining finish. The water heater is brand new. The backyard of this home is quite spacious and features a large patio area and abundant space for gardening and landscaping activities. Included with the home are fencing panels suitable for adding interior fencing or replacing existing panels. This home is located in a quiet area of the subdivision but is within a few minutes reach of Southlands Shopping, E470, and Aurora Reservoir.
